10 SUMMARY
1111 This bill requires the Department of Education to provide for regular instruction in and
1122 opportunities to use cursive handwriting beginning no later than grade 3. The instruction
1133 must be designed to enable students to demonstrate competency in cursive handwriting by
1144 the end of grade 5.
